The agent may:
- Create new feature folders and skeleton files.  
- Write unit tests and minimal e2e tests.  
- Generate PR descriptions with WCAG criteria references.  
- Update `/docs` with examples or notes.  
- Generate compliance reports in `/reports/a11y/`.

The agent may NOT:
- Delete files unless explicitly told.  
- Commit untyped or `any`-heavy code.  
- Introduce overlays, DOM-mutation widgets, or quick-fix libraries.